ical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocation":{"title":"MLNUserLocation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocation","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The MLNUserLocation class defines a specific type of annotation that identifies","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the user’s current location. You do not create instances of this class","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"directly. Instead, you retrieve an existing ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" object from the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"userLocation","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property of the map view displayed in your application.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNUserLocation"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView/update":{"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"update","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"update","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol",